Build It + Home Improvement Magazine June 2013


Build It + Home Improvement gives its readers all the information they need to make their dream home covering self-builds, renovations, conversions, plus a range of home improvement extensions, loft conversions, upgrades and repairs. The magazine is unique because it gives readers the practical advice and guidance required to successfully undertake projects. The editorial demonstrates exactly what to do, provides expert tips from reputable industry insiders on how to do it and clear information on what to buy.
